GLOBAL FUND MANAGEMENTIN THE COMMODITY & TECHNOLOGY SECTORS
 A specialist multi-asset manager delivering consistent performance in volatile markets.








Markets


							Commodities are the basic building blocks of global growth and offer a rich and diverse set of investment opportunities. The main markets we cover are Energy, Metals and Agriculture. We are also active in the high growth technology space.							


Products


							We provide a range of investment products to private investors, institutions and family offices. These products are designed to deliver directional and relative value opportunities in the commodity and technology markets.							


Team


							The Tellurian team is focused and specialized in commodities and technology. We have extensive experience across all products and we thrive to apply a rigorous risk management methodololy.							





